用PayPal Stripe係安全<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&ldquo;據了解，Facebook香港無權處理、擁有、儲存、使用或披露任何Facebook香港或海外用戶資料<br />\n<br />\nFacebook香港辦公室的來電稱，警方曾於今年初多次要求該辦公室交出周庭專頁的資料，但由於有關用戶資料由美國Facebook公司總部持有，並受美國法律保護，不受香港法庭命令約束，因此該辦公室拒絕警方要求，沒有交出任何資料&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200416/IXIM4QK3IZLASBCXTRIAWV7L7I/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200416%2FIXIM4QK3IZLASBCXTRIAWV7L7I%2F&d=5A66RL0pJQ3e97MQjAwjzswxwlTbS8X6vvpFIqFCSYY%3D&h=5e924e13\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20200416%2FIXIM4QK3IZLASBCXTRIAWV7L7I%2F&h=eae2f1db\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20200416/IXIM4QK3IZLASBCXTRIAWV7L7I/</a>"},{"pid":"35824c0151575cfa8595f6bdaac8829de07079e2","tid":2154200,"uid":58841,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5e61b5c43b09484ac28037720e01b6e1dea8b67f","tid":2154200,"uid":201605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f51b44d6d0b36a4247734e9654ecf0f108ca27aa","tid":2154200,"uid":123774,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T05:30:38.000Z","msg":"總之眾籌用paypal或Stripe<br />\n唔好裸跑bank transfer"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T06:46:54.000Z","msg":"PayPal 好似係香港有註冊<br />\n港共執法部門可能攞到料"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-13T07:02:38.000Z","msg":"咪9UP得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}